&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.marinemanagement.org.uk/contacts/local.htm"&gt;Local &lt;abbr title="Marine Management Organisation"&gt;MMO&lt;/abbr&gt; office contact details on the &lt;abbr title="Marine Management Organisation"&gt;MMO&lt;/abbr&gt; website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.defra.gov.uk/environment/marine/wwo/ifca"&gt;IFCA information and district maps on the Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.marinemanagement.org.uk/fisheries/monitoring/documents/code-harbour.pdf"&gt;Download the code of conduct for vessel inspections in harbour from the &lt;abbr title="Marine Management Organisation"&gt;MMO&lt;/abbr&gt; website (PDF, 45KB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.marinemanagement.org.uk/fisheries/monitoring/documents/code-sea.pdf"&gt;Download the vessel inspection at sea code of conduct from the &lt;abbr title="Marine Management Organisation"&gt;MMO&lt;/abbr&gt; website (PDF, 43KB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.defra.gov.uk/environment/marine/wwo/ifca/"&gt;IFCA information on the &lt;abbr title="Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs"&gt;Defra&lt;/abbr&gt; website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
